body.description: Get ready to create your wonderful works of art with the Gabby’s Dollhouse Deluxe Craft Doll playset! Featuring an exclusive Gabby Girl figure, with her artists apron, and an exclusive Baby Box cat figure, this one-of-a-kind arts & crafts playset comes with a magic reveal water pad, a water brush pen, a paint bucket to hold water and three activity sheets, to help you create your masterpieces! Join Gabby and Baby Box Cat, as the three of you work together to relive your favorite artistic moments from the hit Netflix series, Gabby’s Dollhouse, then use your imagination to create entirely new pretend play adventures of your own with the Gabby Deluxe Craft Doll playset! Gabby’s Dollhouse toys, plush toys, toy figures and playsets are educational toys that make great gifts for kids, ages 3 and up, as these toys for girls and boys develop creativity and motor skills through exciting pretend play!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: DreamWorks Gabby’s Dollhouse Gabby Deluxe Craft Doll Join Gabby and Baby Box Cat, from the hit NETFLIX show Gabby’s Dollhouse, as the three of you work together to create your artistic masterpieces! This set includes an 8-inch Gabby Craft Doll, Baby Box Cat figure, and everything you need to create your very own works of art: a water activated drawing pad, a foam tipped water brush pen, a bucket to hold your water and even three activity sheets to use as inspiration when creating your masterpieces! Get ready to use your imagination and enjoy endless hours of artistic fun, with the Gabby Deluxe Craft Doll! Includes: 1 Gabby Doll 1 Baby Box Cat Figure 1 Water Brush 1 Pad with Water Reveal Label 1 Apron 1 Bucket 3 Activity Sheets

Exclusive Gabby Doll The Gabby Deluxe Craft Doll comes with an exclusive Gabby Girl doll, standing 8-inches tall and wearing her rainbow-kitty shirt and magical cat ears, along with her cat-tastic friend Baby Box Cat! Featuring authentic design and styling, Gabby and Baby Box Cat look just like they do in the show! Create Artwork Create works of art with the Gabby’s Dollhouse Deluxe Craft Doll playset! Featuring a magic reveal water pad, a water brush pen, a water bucket and three activity sheets, dip the pen in water and draw on the water pad to create your masterpiece! Let the pad dry and start all over again! Learning Through Play Along with learning to create art, develop your fine motor skills and early writing skills, while reliving your favorite artistic moments from the hit NETFLIX series, then use your imagination to create entirely new pretend play adventures of your own with the Gabby Deluxe Craft Doll playset!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars wonderful addition to any child's toy collection
reviews.reviewText: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐The 8-inch Gabby Girl Doll has captured my heart and earned a glowing five-star review! This adorable doll has quickly become a cherished companion for my little one, and for good reason.What sets the Gabby Girl Doll apart is its charming design and exceptional quality. From the lifelike features to the attention to detail in the outfit, every aspect of this doll exudes charm and craftsmanship. It's evident that a lot of love and care went into creating this delightful companion.I appreciate the size of the doll, as it's perfect for little hands to hold and play with. The soft body and movable limbs add to the interactive experience, sparking imagination and creativity during playtime.Overall, the 8-inch Gabby Girl Doll is a wonderful addition to any child's toy collection. Its charm, quality, and interactive features make it a five-star choice that brings joy and delight to playtime. ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
